        "title": "Body scrolling ",
        "description": "Scrolling the <body> element is disabled when an offcanvas and its backdrop are visible. Use the data-bs-scroll attribute to enable <body> scrolling.",
        "code": "<button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"offcanvas\" data-bs-target=\"#offcanvasScrolling\" aria-controls=\"offcanvasScrolling\">Enable body scrolling<\/button>\n\n<div class=\"offcanvas offcanvas-start\" data-bs-scroll=\"true\" data-bs-backdrop=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" id=\"offcanvasScrolling\" aria-labelledby=\"offcanvasScrollingLabel\">\n  <div class=\"offcanvas-header\">\n    <h5 class=\"offcanvas-title\" id=\"offcanvasScrollingLabel\">Offcanvas with body scrolling<\/h5>\n    <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"offcanvas\" aria-label=\"Close\"><\/button>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"offcanvas-body\">\n    <p>Try scrolling the rest of the page to see this option in action.<\/p>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>",
        "updated_at": "2024-07-02 11:43:28"
    }
